archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: Security Control Map - Website Audience
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This view displays which controls in the original Security Baseline Release 2 that have been selected by the CISO to be aimed at a wider audience within Tech Services, which the CISO has stored in a Release 3 document. The controls in the original Security Control Map are still valid, but some of the controls have been pruned with the aim to simplify the number of controls considering the wider non-architect audience.
The controls chosen by the CISO have been tagged with an "Audience" property and colored to specifically show those controls that are the focus in the CISO's latest document.
